description: Hot Dog Ninja is swiftly attacking every appetite all throughout northern Georgia! Locals just love Landon Brockmeyer and his cart full of big, juicy all-beef dogs and sausages, which are perfect the perfect munch for any occasion; school functions, birthday parties, weddings, church events, and anything else that's going on in your life.Let your friends and family feast on Landon’s craveable selection of specialty dogs, including favorites like The Chilinator with chili, cheese, jalapenos, and sour cream, The Fat Greek with tzatziki sauce, feta, kalamata olives, Soul Slaw with slow and sriracha mayo, and so much more! All with a side of warm, friendly service. Once you try a taste of any of these dogs, you too will be jonesing for your next delicious fix from Hot Dog Ninja.
name: Hot Dog Ninja
